IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Linda L. DORR and Fred L. Dorr Upon the Petition of Linda L. Dorr, Petitioner-Appellant, And Concerning Fred L. Dorr, Respondent-Appellee. No. 17-2023 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Linda Dorr appeals the district court's decree as to the spousal support award, property division, and denial of attorney fees in a marriage dissolution decree. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
